OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"We cannot see a repetition of
OL,7,Fprecious funds being beamed out across
OL,8,Fthe spectrum to those who do not
OL,9,Frequire help.
OL,11,F"This approach is all the more
OL,12,Fimportant when our report shows some
OL,13,Fhouseholds remain exposed, at a time
OL,14,Fwhen the UK's electricity bills appear
OL,15,Fworld-beatingly high and debt weighs
OL,16,Fdown bill-payers' finances to an
OL,17,Falarming degree."
