OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,FThe report read: "We remain concerned
OL,7,Fthat even after the crisis has
OL,8,Fsubsided, UK electricity bills are the
OL,9,Fhighest of the countries providing
OL,10,Fcomparable data to the International
OL,11,FEnergy Association.
OL,13,F"The UK had the highest electricity
OL,14,Fprice out of 25 countries reporting
OL,15,Fboth domestic and industrial
OL,16,Felectricity prices in 2023, (including
OL,17,Ftaxes and levies) and electricity is
OL,18,Fcurrently four-times more expensive
OL,19,Fthan gas.
OL,26,@nD@ROUuD@AOU
