OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"Despite repeated promises, the
OL,7,Fdepartment has delayed taking action
OL,8,Fto rebalance energy prices by shifting
OL,9,Fthe cost of environmental levies from
OL,10,Felectricity to gas.
OL,12,F"In addition, the department is
OL,13,Freviewing how electricity prices are
OL,14,Fset for households so that they can
OL,15,Fbenefit from cheaper rates if demand
OL,16,Fis low or when the weather means more
OL,17,Fenergy is produced.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
