OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"But this review has been running for
OL,7,Fthree years and remains on an
OL,8,Funcertain timetable, meaning it is
OL,9,Funclear when consumers will start to
OL,10,Fsee the benefits through reductions to
OL,11,Ftheir bills."
OL,13,FThe PAC said the DESNZ must do more to
OL,14,Fconvince Parliament that it has a
OL,15,F"robust plan" for ensuring security of
OL,16,Fenergy supply amid increasing global
OL,17,Ftensions.
OL,19,FAn Ofgem spokesperson said: "We know
OL,20,Fthe cost of energy is a huge challenge
OL,21,Ffor many households.
