OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"If anyone is worried about paying
OL,7,Ftheir bills, we urge them to contact
OL,8,Ftheir supplier or groups like Citizens
OL,9,FAdvice to make sure they're getting
OL,10,Fall the help they can. Switching or
OL,11,Ffixing tariffs now, where possible,
OL,12,Fcould also help consumers to bring
OL,13,Fcosts down.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
