OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"We've introduced tougher rules to
OL,7,Fmake sure energy companies do more to
OL,8,Fspot the signs when a customer may be
OL,9,Fstruggling and step in to offer
OL,10,Fsupport, including working out
OL,11,Faffordable payment plans and providing
OL,12,Femergency credit to reduce the risk of
OL,13,Fself-disconnection.
OL,15,F"We have also made pre-payment meters
OL,16,Fthe cheapest way to pay for energy,
OL,17,Fand are consulting on plans to
OL,18,Fintroduce a scheme that could provide
OL,19,Fdirect support to those struggling
OL,20,Fwith unmanageable levels of debt.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
