OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"We continually monitor the service
OL,7,Fsuppliers are providing to their
OL,8,Fcustomers and where they are falling
OL,9,Fshort, we hold them to account.
OL,10,FHowever, the issue of debt is one that
OL,11,Frequires action from everyone across
OL,12,Fthe sector and government."
OL,14,FA Department for Energy Security and
OL,15,FNet Zero spokesperson said: "Our
OL,16,Fmission for clean power is the only
OL,17,Fway to protect UK billpayers from
OL,18,Ffuture price shocks.
