OL,3,CGovernment urged to improve response
OL,4,Cto 'world-beatingly high' energy bills
OL,6,F"The 2022-23 energy crisis, which saw
OL,7,Fsky-high energy bills and put pressure
OL,8,Fon households and businesses across
OL,9,Fthe country, was a product of our
OL,10,Freliance on gas for heating and
OL,11,Fpowering our homes. We will bring down
OL,12,Fbills for good by moving towards a
OL,13,Fclean, homegrown power system that we
OL,14,Fcontrol.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
